OL,3,CMan jailed after bomb hoax call to
OL,4,Ccity synagogue
OL,6,FA man who made a bomb hoax call to a
OL,7,Fsynagogue in Leeds, just days after a
OL,8,Fterror attack in Manchester, has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FMarkel Ible, 32, called Sinai
OL,12,FSynagogue in Roundhay, on October 6,
OL,13,Fclaiming to have left a bomb that was
OL,14,Fdue to go off the following day.
OL,16,FIt came four days after two people
OL,17,Fwere killed in an attack on the Heaton
OL,18,FPark Hebrew Synagogue in Manchester.
