OL,3,CMan jailed after bomb hoax call to
OL,4,Ccity synagogue
OL,6,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, and Adrian Daulby,
OL,7,F53, died and three other men were
OL,8,Finjured when Jihad Al-Shamie, 35,
OL,9,Ftargeted the place of worship on the
OL,10,Fholy day of Yom Kippur.
OL,12,FHe drove his car at those gathering
OL,13,Fbefore attacking others with a knife
OL,14,Fand trying to storm the synagogue.
OL,16,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said he
OL,17,F"intended to sow panic and fear."
OL,19,FHe was charged the day after the call
OL,20,Fwas reported to police.
