OL,3,CMan jailed after bomb hoax call to
OL,4,Ccity synagogue
OL,6,FIble, of St Martins Gardens, Leeds,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to making a bomb hoax
OL,8,Fcall. On Wednesday, he was jailed for
OL,9,Ften months at Leeds Crown Court.
OL,11,FDave Rich, from the Jewish charity
OL,12,FCommunity Security Trust, said the
OL,13,Fhoax was "cruel and calculated."
OL,15,F"Ible's hoax call was not just
OL,16,Freckless, it was cruel and calculated.
OL,17,FThe hoax call was designed to spread
OL,18,Fpanic and distress at a time when the
OL,19,Fcommunity was already feeling
OL,20,Fvulnerable."
